                    <span>While working on an assignment for a graduate level managerial communications class, I browsed several books on business presentations.  Mr. Leech's book was the one I chose to use. It provides a wealth of  information, while being very readable. Reading this book added to the  knowledge I gained from the class. This book will become a valuble part of  my business library.</span>
                  
              
